Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) - The paper focuses on energy-efficient image detection for computer vision applications, which is a core topic in this sub-category.
2. cs.ET (Embedded Systems) - The paper discusses hardware implementation of CV processors, which is a common topic in this sub-category.
3. cs.AR (Hardware Architecture) - The paper proposes an ADC design for energy-efficient vision processors, which is a topic related to hardware architecture.
4. cs.EM (Electromagnetics) - The paper may involve electromagnetic considerations in the design of the proposed ADC architecture.
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with image detection and processing, which is a topic related to multimedia applications.
